    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "14, 15. Thou shalt not oppress an hired servant that is poor and needyâ€”Hired servants in the East are paid at the close of the day; and for a master to defraud the laborer of his hire, or to withhold it wrongfully for a night, might have subjected a poor man with his family to suffering and was therefore an injustice to be avoided (Le 19:13).",
        "children": []
