        "text": "Leviticus 19:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", with special reference to the distress of the poor man. \"And to it (his wages) he lifts up his soul:\" i.e., he feels a longing for it. \"Lifts up his soul:\" as in ",
        "children": []
